      "message": "FWIU you are concerned with usage of keepAlive here. FWIU you reason you have it here is that there are some simple functions (not observables) that need tests too. If so, why can\u0027t we have a simple function .computeTests() for simple functions and an observable .tests for observables?\n\n  public function computeAllTests() { ... }\n  @computed get allTest(): readonly ReadonlyTest[]{ return this.computeAllTests(); }\n\nwould it address the memory leak concern?",
