      "writtenOn": "2020-03-23T00:39:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In that case, this.computeAllTests() will need to traverse all descendant node every time it is called instead of using the cache.\nAnd tests will be accessed that way a lot more frequently than using this.allTests (typically in a handler of some event).\nSince this.allTests only depends on property on this node or its descendants, keepAlive should be safe to use here.",
